cs.LG, cs.SD, cs.SY, cs.CL, cs.AI 

The paper discusses the development of a visual interactive web application for interpreting the internal reasoning of deep learning models trained on audio data. This work falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) as it deals with the development of a tool for understanding and debugging machine learning models. Additionally, it involves the use of sequential data (audio) which falls under the sub-category of signal processing (cs.SD) and systems and control (cs.SY). The paper also discusses the need for transparency and interpretability in deep learning models, which falls under the sub-category of natural language processing (cs.CL) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
